    <briefdescription>
<para>An authentication implementation for a Flight service. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Authentication includes both an initial negotiation and a per-call token validation. Implementations may choose to use either or both mechanisms. An implementation may need to track some state, e.g. a mapping of client tokens to authenticated identities. </para>    </detaileddescription>
